"'''CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:10:05 Edition'''" was an in-universe [[CIS Shadowfeed (Insider)|''CIS Shadowfeed'']] issue published in [[Star Wars Insider 71|''Star Wars Insider'' 71]].

{{Magazine-stub|article}}

==Contents==
*''Neimoidians Double Conscription Rate''
*''Jedi Watchgroup on the HoloNet''

==Continuity==
This article was mistakenly printed with the incorrect in-universe date of 14:9:15, which corresponded with the date of the previous article released in [[Star Wars Insider 70]], [[CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:9:15 Edition|CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:9:15]].

